   Cao, Limin, Hengyang Normal Univ, Coll Life Sci \& Environm, Hengyang 421008, Peoples R China.
   Newman, Mark F.; de Craene, Louis P. Ronse, Royal Bot Garden Edinburgh, 20A Inverleith Row, Edinburgh EH3 5LR, Midlothian, Scotland.
   Kirchoff, Bruce K., Univ N Carolina, Dept Biol, Greensboro, NC 27402 USA.},
